node.text:
Waterfront homes in the Turkish town of Göcek, Fethiye 🚤 Get your photos posted in our account, apply for a feature visiting tourfervor.com 👉🏼 the link is in our bio: @tourfervor
Would you ever live in a place like this?

📽 @bugunnereyegidelim (Tüm Hakları Saklıdır)
📍Göcek, Fethiye, Turkey
🎶 Tommee Profitt - In The End (Mellen Gi Remix) [feat. Fleurie]

node.text:
The beautiful landscapes of Skageflå, Norway 🏞 We can promote your photos in our account. Check the link in our bio for instructions: @tourfervor

📽 @varvik
🚶🏼‍♀️@gossegoss
🐶 @roamingpuppers
📍 Skageflå, Geiranger, Norway
🎶 What A Wonderful World - Louis Armstrong

How cute is Rasta? 🥰 Apply for a feature following the link in our bio and we will publish your photos in our account: @tourfervor

The adventure pup from Switzerland? Tag someone who loves @nature as him!
Photos and videos by @michelphotographych w/ @rastawhiteshepherd

Flower mantises are those species of praying mantises that mimic flowers. Their coloration is an example of aggressive mimicry, a form of camouflage in which a predator's colours and patterns lure prey.
